Certiorari Granted.

No. 536. Compagna et al. v. Hiatt, Warden. C. A. 5th Cir. A. Walton Nall and Ifm. Scott Stewart for petitioners. Solicitor General Perlman, Assistant Attorney General Mclnerney, Robert S. Erdahl and Philip R. Monahan for respondent.
